8. Python IDLE

Comes with Python installation
A simple Python editor + interpreter

How to Open:

Search Python in Start Menu
Click IDLE

✅ Good for small programs
❌ Not ideal for big projects

9. Why Do We Need an IDE?
For big projects like:

Web Applications
AI / Machine Learning
Desktop Applications

We need:

Code editor
Run button
Debugging
Project management

✅ This is provided by an IDE (Integrated Development Environment)

